TYPE_MANAGED_ATTRIBUTE

public static final java.lang.String TYPE_MANAGED_ATTRIBUTE
Gag. We should never ever have used package prefixes on our type names but now there is UI infrastrure that assumes that even though no one writing forms manually remembers. ManagedAttribute has been a special case, I'm not sure how widespread it is but until we can asssess the mess, do normalization in the UI layer since many fields will have used just "ManagedAttribute".
